  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-01 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This synthetic adversarial package targets W-EP-01: the bound claim appears richly described and the validation results carry full provenance, but the Claim node itself lacks prov:wasDerivedFrom, making it an orphan with no structured evidentiary derivation link.",
